data.description: Welcome to this remarkable 3-bedroom home with a bonus room plus office! Sits on the 3rd fairway at Lakeview Golf Course. This home combines spacious living areas with the convenience of a larger garage, allowing ample space for your vehicles, storage, golf cart and even a workshop. All grab bars and Ada functions are easily removed. Large closets and storage galore throughout this home. Upstairs is perfect for extra suite or out of town guests needing their own space. Summers on the patio are perfection for those sunsets. Enjoy golf course living and walk to club house activities. 2 fireplaces, one in living and one in primary suite, double doors from suite to enjoy the outdoors. ADA bathroom amenities as well. New gutter cover system for easy maintenance. Brand new exterior paint.  ***Ask about a flooring allowance!
